These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, fanta, hot-chocolate, juice
4 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, pony, bird, frog
1. the owner of the frog is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
2. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the pony##1
3. the person drinking juice is in an odd position##4
4. the owner of the bird is on the left or right of the owner of the frog##3
5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Beverage   | soy-milk | fanta | juice | hot-chocolate |
| Pet        | guinea-pig | pony   | frog | bird    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, epic, documentary, family
There are 4 different nationalities: mexican, canadian, pakistani, indonesian
1. the person watching epic movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
2. the mexican is on the left of the pakistani##1
3. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
4. the mexican is the person watching action movies##1
5. the canadian is on the right of the pakistani##1
6. the mexican is the person watching action movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  | epic  | family |
| Nationality   | indonesian    | mexican | pakistani | canadian    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, broccoli, spinach, radish
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, disaster, thriller, comedy
1. the person eating radish is on the left or right of the person watching comedy movies##3
2. the person eating spinach is in an even position##4
3. the person watching comedy movies is on the left or right of the person eating broccoli##3
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
5. the person watching scientific movies is in an odd position##4
6. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Food          | radish | spinach | broccoli    | banana      |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller        | comedy     | scientific | disaster |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: photography, puzzles, board-games, skydiving
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: electronic, salsa, pop, jazz
1. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the fan of electronic and the fan of jazz##2
2. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
3. the fan of pop is in an odd position##4
4. the fan of salsa is on the left of the fan of jazz##1
5. the fan of salsa is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | skydiving | photography | puzzles | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | pop       | electronic   | salsa    | jazz  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: r&b, indie, d&b, house
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, spanish, french, pakistani
1. the fan of d&b is on the right of the pakistani##1
2. the spanish is the fan of house##1
3. the french is on the right of the fan of r&b##1
4. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
5. the fan of d&b is in an odd position##4
6. the argentine is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | r&b    | d&b   | house       |
| Nationality   | argentine | pakistani | french | spanish |

