.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: animation, superhero, adventure, drama
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, snowmobile, helicopter, skateboard
1. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
3. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
4. the person driving the skateboard is the person watching animation movies##1
5. the person watching drama movies is on the left or right of the person driving the bus##3
6. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person driving the bus##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |    2    |    3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | drama | adventure | superhero    |
| Transport     | skateboard | helicopter  | bus     | snowmobile |

