.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-8::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  designer, electrician, librarian, lawyer
4 different pets are kept: lizard, chinchilla, frog, turtle
1. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the electrician##3
2. the lawyer is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the lawyer##3
4. the lawyer is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
5. the designer is between the lawyer and the electrician##2
6. the owner of the chinchilla is in an odd position##4
7. the owner of the chinchilla is between the designer and the owner of the frog##2
8. the designer is on the left or right of the electrician##3

.:: Answer ::.
|       |   1   |     2      |    3    |        4        |
| Job   | electrician | designer      | lawyer | librarian |
| Pet   | lizard  | turtle | chinchilla    | frog            |

