4 different pets are kept: dog, horse, hedgehog, rabbit
1. the person eating papaya is on the left or right of the person eating lime##3
2. the person eating lime is on the right of the person eating potato##1
3. the owner of the dog is between the owner of the horse and the person eating papaya##2
4. the owner of the dog is in an odd position##4
5. the person eating papaya is the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Food   | blueberry | potato   | lime | papaya |
| Pet    | rabbit     | horse | dog     | hedgehog  |

