.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, water, fanta, 7up
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, country, pop, classical
1. the person drinking iced-tea is the fan of classical##1
2. the fan of ambient is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
3. the fan of classical is between the fan of ambient and the person drinking fanta##2
4. the person drinking iced-tea is in an odd position##4
5. the fan of classical is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
6. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan of country##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| Beverage      | water       | fanta   | iced-tea | 7up |
| Music-Genre   | pop | country | classical        | ambient    |

