.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-11::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, cola, lemonade, iced-tea
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, badminton, lacrosse, ice-hockey
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person drinking 7up##1
3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left or right of the person drinking lemonade##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |    2    |     3      |    4     |
| Beverage   | 7up   | iced-tea   | cola      | lemonade      |
| Sport      | badminton | lacrosse | ice-hockey | snowboarding |

