.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-12::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, peas, corn, cucumber
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: rock, funk, r&b, dubstep
1. the fan of r&b is on the left of the fan of rock##1
2. the fan of r&b is in an even position##4
3. the person eating peas is in an even position##4
4. the person eating pomegranate is on the far right##1
5. the person eating corn is between the fan of funk and the fan of r&b##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Food          | cucumber | peas  | corn  | pomegranate |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep  | r&b | rock | funk   |

