.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-15::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, hiking, reading, traveling
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: tennis, handball, swimming, golf
1. the person who's hobby is singing is between the person who's sport is tennis and the person who's hobby is hiking##2
2. the person who's hobby is reading is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person who's sport is golf##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is in an odd position##4
6. the person who's sport is swimming is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |       2       |       3       |      4       |
| Hobby   | traveling | hiking         | singing   | reading |
| Sport   | swimming    | handball | golf | tennis   |

