.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-16::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: drawing, cooking, photography, sudoku
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, handball, tennis, rowing
1. the person who's sport is rowing is the person who's hobby is photography##1
2. the person who's sport is tennis is the person who's hobby is drawing##1
3. the person who's sport is handball is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
4. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is sudoku##3
5. the person who's hobby is drawing is in an even position##4
6. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |      2      |     3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | photography    | sudoku |
| Sport   | sailing   | tennis  | rowing | handball     |

