.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, soy-milk, mirinda, hot-chocolate
There 4 different types of food: onion, zucchini, pear, cauliflower
1. the person eating zucchini is on the far left##1
2. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the person drinking juice##3
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating pear is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
5. the person eating cauliflower is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
6. the person eating pear is in an even position##4
7. the person eating onion is the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate | juice    | mirinda       | soy-milk |
| Food       | zucchini  | pear | cauliflower | onion  |

