.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-19::.
There are 4 different nationalities: french, russian, brazilian, british
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, snowmobile, car, train
1. the french is on the left of the british##1
2. the person driving the car is on the left or right of the person driving the taxi##3
3. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the car##1
4. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the brazilian##1
5. the french is on the right of the person driving the car##1
6. the person driving the taxi is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3     |     4     |
| Nationality   | russian | brazilian | french  | british |
| Transport     | taxi      | car       | snowmobile | train     |

