.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-20::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, bartender, firefighter, coach
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, motorbike, airplane
1. the bartender is in an even position##4
2. the bartender is on the left or right of the person driving the tram##3
3. the person driving the scooter is between the librarian and the person driving the tram##2
4. the bartender is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the coach##1
6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Job         | librarian | firefighter   | coach | bartender |
| Transport   | airplane          | scooter | tram         | motorbike  |

 